text.tspan: Women's civil society participation index, World
Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem, weighted by countries' populations. It captures the extent to
which women can discuss political issues, participate in civil society organizations, and are represented among
journalists. It ranges from 0 to 1 (most participatory).
Data source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13); Gapminder (v6); HYDE (v3.2); UN (2022)
